snippet.title: Dark is the Night Intro
snippet.description:
The official Intro Trailer of the first update to Coreborn, Dark is the Night.

🎮 WISHLIST NOW on Steam: https://bit.ly/WishlistCoreborn

💬 Join Coreborn Discord for updates and playtests: https://discord.gg/coreborn

Coreborn, initially coming to Early Access on PC, will be a multiplayer survival game set in the open world of Ultracore. Build, grow, and defend your town. Survive the elements and Sorgoth’s onslaught. Cooperate as you go on adventures.

Follow Coreborn
Twitter | Instagram | TikTok: @playCoreborn
